Input- 
User ( id, username, password, role)
Role ( id, name, user)

Process - 
1. Give an option to the user either to sign up or login 
2. if the user choose signUp, create a user with role that already exists
3. store the new user and give it the role
4. if login the user should put the user name and password
5.validating the log in 
6. Add a new role
7. add a role to a user
8. add a user to a role
9. validate a user so that it won't be added to a role twice
10. validate a same role cannot be added to a same user twice
11. login that will use a password a user name 


 

